}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== ===Specifications=== *WLAN: 2T2R (802.11 b/g/n) *LAN: 4x FE (10/100 Base-TX), 2x FXS (RJ11) *Modulation: QPSK, 16/64QAM, OFDMA *Standarts: 802.16e Wave 2 (2.5~2.7 GHz) *Antennas: (Wi-Fi/Mobile WiMAX) :2x external antenna for Wi-Fi :3x internal panels antenna for Mobile WiMAX (9dBi) *Power (rad.): Wi-Fi <100 mW, WiMAX <250 mW (27dBm) *Power (req.): 12W *Dimension: 227x155x44 mm *Weight: 738g
